{"tha-ap403:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap403:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap403:0.3":"Tissametteyyattheraapadana ","tha-ap403:1.1":"“Pabbharakutam nissaya, ","tha-ap403:1.2":"sobhito nama tapaso; ","tha-ap403:1.3":"Pavattaphalam bhunjitva, ","tha-ap403:1.4":"vasati pabbatantare. ","tha-ap403:2.1":"Aggim darum aharitva, ","tha-ap403:2.2":"ujjalesim aham tada; ","tha-ap403:2.3":"Uttamattham gavesanto, ","tha-ap403:2.4":"brahmalokupapattiya. ","tha-ap403:3.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap403:3.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap403:3.3":"Mamuddharitukamo so, ","tha-ap403:3.4":"agacchi mama santike. ","tha-ap403:4.1":"‘Kim karosi mahapunna, ","tha-ap403:4.2":"dehi me aggidarukam; ","tha-ap403:4.3":"Ahamaggim paricare, ","tha-ap403:4.4":"tato me suddhi hohiti’. ","tha-ap403:5.1":"‘Subhaddako tvam manuje, ","tha-ap403:5.2":"devate tvam pajanasi; ","tha-ap403:5.3":"Tuvam aggim paricara, ","tha-ap403:5.4":"handa te aggidarukam’. ","tha-ap403:6.1":"Tato kattham gahetvana, ","tha-ap403:6.2":"aggim ujjalayi jino; ","tha-ap403:6.3":"Na tattha kattham pajjhayi, ","tha-ap403:6.4":"patiheram mahesino. ","tha-ap403:7.1":"‘Na te aggi pajjalati, ","tha-ap403:7.2":"ahuti te na vijjati; ","tha-ap403:7.3":"Niratthakam vatam tuyham, ","tha-ap403:7.4":"aggim paricarassu me’. ","tha-ap403:8.1":"‘Kidiso so mahavira, ","tha-ap403:8.2":"aggi tava pavuccati; ","tha-ap403:8.3":"Mayhampi kathayassetam, ","tha-ap403:8.4":"ubho paricaramase’. ","tha-ap403:9.1":"‘Hetudhammanirodhaya, ","tha-ap403:9.2":"kilesasamanaya ca; ","tha-ap403:9.3":"Issamacchariyam hitva, ","tha-ap403:9.4":"tayo ete mamahuti’. ","tha-ap403:10.1":"‘Kidiso tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap403:10.2":"katham gottosi marisa; ","tha-ap403:10.3":"Acarapatipatti te, ","tha-ap403:10.4":"balham kho mama ruccati’. ","tha-ap403:11.1":"‘Khattiyamhi kule jato, ","tha-ap403:11.2":"abhinnaparamim gato; ","tha-ap403:11.3":"Sabbasavaparikkhino, ","tha-ap403:11.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo’. ","tha-ap403:12.1":"‘Yadi buddhosi sabbannu, ","tha-ap403:12.2":"pabhankara tamonuda; ","tha-ap403:12.3":"Namassissami tam deva, ","tha-ap403:12.4":"dukkhassantakaro tuvam’. ","tha-ap403:13.1":"Pattharitvajinacammam, ","tha-ap403:13.2":"nisidanamadasaham; ","tha-ap403:13.3":"Nisida natha sabbannu, ","tha-ap403:13.4":"upatthissamaham tuvam. ","tha-ap403:14.1":"Nisidi bhagava tattha, ","tha-ap403:14.2":"ajinamhi suvitthate; ","tha-ap403:14.3":"Nimantayitva sambuddham, ","tha-ap403:14.4":"pabbatam agamasaham. ","tha-ap403:15.1":"Kharibharanca puretva, ","tha-ap403:15.2":"tindukaphalamaharim; ","tha-ap403:15.3":"Madhuna yojayitvana, ","tha-ap403:15.4":"phalam buddhassadasaham. ","tha-ap403:16.1":"Mama nijjhayamanassa, ","tha-ap403:16.2":"paribhunji tada jino; ","tha-ap403:16.3":"Tattha cittam pasadesim, ","tha-ap403:16.4":"pekkhanto lokanayakam. ","tha-ap403:17.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap403:17.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap403:17.3":"Mamassame nisiditva, ","tha-ap403:17.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap403:18.1":"‘Yo mam phalena tappesi, ","tha-ap403:18.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap403:18.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap403:18.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap403:19.1":"Pancavisatikkhattum so, ","tha-ap403:19.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap403:19.3":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap403:19.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap403:20.1":"Tassa sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap403:20.2":"pubbakammasamangino; ","tha-ap403:20.3":"Annam pananca vatthanca, ","tha-ap403:20.4":"sayananca maharaham. ","tha-ap403:21.1":"Punnakammena samyutta, ","tha-ap403:21.2":"nibbattissanti tavade; ","tha-ap403:21.3":"Sada pamudito cayam, ","tha-ap403:21.4":"bhavissati anamayo. ","tha-ap403:22.1":"Upapajjati yam yonim, ","tha-ap403:22.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap403:22.3":"Sabbattha sukhito hutva, ","tha-ap403:22.4":"manussattam gamissati. ","tha-ap403:23.1":"Ajjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap403:23.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap403:23.3":"Sambuddham upagantvana, ","tha-ap403:23.4":"araha so bhavissati’. ","tha-ap403:24.1":"Yato sarami attanam, ","tha-ap403:24.2":"yato pattosmi vinnutam; ","tha-ap403:24.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap403:24.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap403:25.1":"Varadhammamanuppatto, ","tha-ap403:25.2":"ragadose samuhanim; ","tha-ap403:25.3":"Sabbasavaparikkhino, ","tha-ap403:25.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap403:26.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap403:26.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap403:26.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap403:26.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap403:27.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap403:27.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap403:27.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap403:27.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap403:28.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap403:28.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap403:28.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap403:28.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap403:29.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tissametteyyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap403:30.1":"Tissametteyyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}